eate a book around my unique mechanism. And also come up with my own language terms. For everything so that it is not seen as a copyright infringement or a direct Duplicate, from any of the other models.I am taking the principles of the many different ways to explore personality but im not claiming to be a medical or mental health professional. I just want to deep dice into the tools and make my own platform. And actually no one even includes narcissism, and when we start talking about business, leadership,  Self identiy , and working with others, narcissism is one of the areas that caused the most pain and grief, and there are the fewest amount of resources to help with that. Separately we should find a way to deal with this without the direct use if the word narcissism as it can be triggering and i dont want controversy in my digital programs . So we need another way to incorporate challenging personalities like narcissism in a way that brings positive transformation   some of the trainings from youtube channels like @MedCircle @DoctorRamani@SurvivingNarcissism @MentalHealness and I'll help you build a $500k/month profit, 95% margin business with your Strategic AI Personality Assessment platform. Let me research the narcissism/challenging personality aspects first, then create a comprehensive moat-building strategy with unique language and mechanisms. Using Tool | Parallel Search narcissism in workplace leadership 2024 toxic leadership personality assessment business MedCircle narcissism training content DoctorRamani workplace narcissism resources SurvivingNarcissism business applications MentalHealness personality framework challenging personality types workplace assessment dark triad personality business leadership View Using Tool | Parallel Search MedCircle @DoctorRamani YouTube narcissism business applications SurvivingNarcissism @MentalHealness workplace personalities training dark triad business leadership assessment framework 2024 challenging personalities 